_sText:
De_persia

this is my 3rd map that I have created. It takes place in a market of Persia. It is a bomb defuse and is very tricky. The best strategy for this map is to keep yourself hidden and guarded. Poking out may cost you your life. Bomb sites are very open and vulnurable, and rushing may only get you killed. HAVE FUN

Inspector_Gadget16
